                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                透過各種商務情境如接待客戶, 銷售產品, 安排物流,及商貿糾紛之模擬, 進行商務美語口說介紹及演練, 其次按照國際貿易之交易流程, 自客戶招攬至索賠,催收,有系統的介紹各項貿易英文書信之寫作

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                This course will introduce oral business communication through the situation of customer reception, sales / promotion, logistics/scheduling, and problems/solution. Moreover, the second part of the course will introduce business writing technique according to the process of international business trade ,from customer solicitation to claims and collection of bills.











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





                                1 講義及ppt2 參考用書:- 搞定進階商務口說(Advanced Business Communication)總編審王復國, 作者:Dana Forsythe,  貝塔語言出版- 國際商務英文-貿易書信寫作及實務(International Business English): 呂金交著, 眾文圖書公司出版











                                課程要求
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Requirement
                            





《 上課要求 》
                                上課守則(Class Discipline)1: Please switch your mobile phone to silent mode.2 Feel free go to the restroom any time you need it.3 Class sign up may be required 2-3 times without notice.(10 % of your performance)4 Please advise me at least 1 day in advance if you need to take a break for the session  ( use i can)






《 報告要求 》






